name: Sample Report 3
query: select tabInvoices.gst_number as `GSTIN of supplier`, tabInvoices.legal_name as `Trade/Legal name of the Supplier`, invoice_number as `Invoice number`, invoice_type as `Invoice type`, invoice_date as `Invoice Date`, item_value_after_gst as `Invoice Value (₹)`, tabcompany.location as `Place of supply`, tabItems.gst_rate as `Rate`, tabItems.item_value as `Taxable Value (₹)`,tabItems.igst_amount as 'Integrated Tax  (₹)', tabItems.cgst_amount as `Central Tax (₹)`,tabItems.sgst_amount as `State/UT tax (₹)` from tabInvoices JOIN tabItems ON tabInvoices.name = tabItems.parent JOIN tabcompany ON tabInvoices.company = tabcompany.name order by invoice_number;
